<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.1.2">
<l>kaṭṭuraikki ṟāmarainiṉ kaṇpātaṅ kaiyovvā</l>
<l>cuṭṭuraitta naṉpoṉṉuṉ ṟirumēṉi yoḷiyovvā</l>
<l>toṭṭuraittiv vulakuṉṉaip pukaḻvellām perumpālum</l>
<l>paṭṭuraiyāy puṟkeṉṟē kāṭṭumāl parañcoti</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you tell, lotuses are not equal to your eyes, feet [and] hands.</l>
<l>Good gold that is heated [and] tested is not equal to the light of your luminous/sacred body.</l>
<l>Speaking about suitability, all the great share of all the praise to you in this world</l>
<l>occurs [and] shows itseld pale as word [against your] highest light.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
